        Settlement Extensions in Queensland: What Sellers Need to Know
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A buyer asking for extra time to settle is more common than most sellers expect. Your response to that request has real financial and legal consequences.
      </p>
